# Kakao Local 헬스장 신호 tick — enrich_gym_kakao.py(Kakao Local). 비아파트 ≤50m 헬스장 → gym
# enrichment 사실(source_type='kakao_local')만 write(좌표/canonical 무접촉 → 지문/counts 불변) (gym-kakao).
# 공유 .ingest.lock(C47) 청크 spin-acquire/release로 거래·enrich·poi·unit-type cron과 직렬화·공존.
# Kakao 일쿼터(429/400 code-10) 우아중단 → 다음날 resume(stage='gym_kakao'). 멀티데이·비아파트 집중.
[Unit]
Description=ht-estate Kakao gym signal tick (비아파트, daily)

[Service]
Type=oneshot
User=hyunlord
Group=hyunlord
WorkingDirectory=/home/hyunlord/github/ht-estate/apps/api
Environment=HOME=/home/hyunlord
Environment=PATH=/home/hyunlord/.local/bin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin
# --limit 0=쿼터까지(quota-stop이 다음날 resume). 단지당 2키워드 콜 → --interval throttle.
ExecStart=/home/hyunlord/.local/bin/uv run python scripts/enrich_gym_kakao.py --limit 0 --batch-size 25 --interval 0.1
